item.title: About Me
item.description: I’m a developer based near Philadelphia, PA. I enjoy technology and writing about the things that I’m interested in is one of my favorite ways to learn. Outside of tech and my day job, you’ll probably find me playing World of Warcraft, watching football or soccer, or just hanging out with my family.
